<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[In the end, did Helen kill herself after all? I got the impression that she changed her mind, but I'm not sure. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
