<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/9756891-madhura"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1597069111i/9756891._UX100_CR0,25,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/9756891-madhura">Madhura</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    No she did not kill herself. She realized her daughters were her strength and she would do the right thing and accept the judgement that came with her<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    No she did not kill herself. She realized her daughters were her strength and she would do the right thing and accept the judgement that came with her deeds. She did not kill Mrs Leverton either. Mrs Leverton died as a result of a bad fall and Helen simply chose to hide out in her house since no one would think to look for her there.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
