<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1813888-i-am-finding-it-difficult-to-get-into-this">I am finding it difficult to get into this book. I read and enjoyed &quot;The Lovely Bones&quot; and began &quot;The Almost Moon&quot; with hope. It has taken me ages to reach p31 and when I do read it is in very short bursts as I find it quite overwhelming. Is it worth persisting?</a>
</div>
