<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2532404166745415497">Alice Sebold is the author of three #1 bestselling books, including Lucky, and the novels The Lovely Bones and The Almost Moon. Her work has been translated into more than fifty languages and has appeared in The New York Times and The Guardian, among other publications. She is a member of the National Leadership Council for RAINN.org (Rape, Abuse &amp; Incest National Network). She lives in California</span>
  <span id="freeText2532404166745415497" style="display:none">Alice Sebold is the author of three #1 bestselling books, including Lucky, and the novels The Lovely Bones and The Almost Moon. Her work has been translated into more than fifty languages and has appeared in The New York Times and The Guardian, among other publications. She is a member of the National Leadership Council for RAINN.org (Rape, Abuse &amp; Incest National Network). She lives in California.</span>
